---
---
<section class="mb-16">
  <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 flex items-center gap-4 text-white">
    <span class="text-cyber-cyan text-shadow-neon-cyan">&lt;</span>
    Ключевые проекты
    <span class="text-cyber-cyan text-shadow-neon-cyan">/&gt;</span>
  </h3>

  <div class="space-y-8 relative before:absolute before:inset-0 before:ml-4 md:before:ml-[4.5rem] before:-translate-x-px md:before:mx-auto md:before:translate-x-0 before:h-full before:w-0.5 before:bg-gradient-to-b before:from-transparent before:via-cyber-cyan/50 before:to-transparent">
    
    <!-- Item 1 -->
    <div class="relative flex items-center justify-between md:justify-normal md:odd:flex-row-reverse group is-active">
      <!-- Icon -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-cyber-cyan bg-cyber-bg text-cyber-cyan shadow-[0_0_10px_var(--color-cyber-cyan)] shrink-0 md:order-1 md:group-odd:-translate-x-1/2 md:group-even:translate-x-1/2 ml-0 md:ml-0 z-10 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110">
        <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-cyber-cyan"></div>
      </div>
      <!-- Card -->
      <div class="w-[calc(100%-3rem)] md:w-[calc(50%-2rem)] cyber-border p-6 bg-cyber-bg-light/60 backdrop-blur-sm group-hover:border-cyber-cyan/70 transition-colors ml-4 md:ml-0 md:group-odd:mr-8 md:group-even:ml-8">
        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2 font-orbitron group-hover:text-shadow-neon-cyan transition-all">Telegram Mini App — Конструктор футболок</h4>
        <p class="text-cyber-muted mb-4 text-sm font-sans leading-relaxed">Разработка интерактивного 2D-редактора с полным циклом.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs font-mono">
          <span class="text-cyber-magenta">Vue 3</span>
          <span class="text-cyber-magenta">Nuxt</span>
          <span class="text-cyber-cyan">Konva.js</span>
          <span class="text-cyber-yellow">Node.js</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Item 2 -->
    <div class="relative flex items-center justify-between md:justify-normal md:odd:flex-row-reverse group">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-cyber-magenta bg-cyber-bg text-cyber-magenta shrink-0 md:order-1 md:group-odd:-translate-x-1/2 md:group-even:translate-x-1/2 ml-0 md:ml-0 z-10 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110">
        <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-cyber-magenta"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-[calc(100%-3rem)] md:w-[calc(50%-2rem)] border border-cyber-magenta/30 p-6 bg-cyber-bg-light/60 backdrop-blur-sm group-hover:border-cyber-magenta/70 transition-colors ml-4 md:ml-0 md:group-odd:mr-8 md:group-even:ml-8 relative">
        <div class="absolute -top-[1px] -left-[1px] w-4 h-4 border-t-2 border-l-2 border-cyber-magenta z-10"></div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-[1px] -right-[1px] w-4 h-4 border-b-2 border-r-2 border-cyber-magenta z-10"></div>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2 font-orbitron group-hover:text-shadow-neon-magenta transition-all">CRM для молодёжного движения «Первые»</h4>
        <p class="text-cyber-muted mb-4 text-sm font-sans leading-relaxed">Фронтенд сложной админ-панели с ролевой моделью и таблицами на 10к+.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs font-mono">
          <span class="text-cyber-magenta">Vue 3</span>
          <span class="text-cyber-cyan">Pinia</span>
          <span class="text-cyber-cyan">TypeScript</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Item 3 -->
    <div class="relative flex items-center justify-between md:justify-normal md:odd:flex-row-reverse group">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-cyber-yellow bg-cyber-bg text-cyber-yellow shrink-0 md:order-1 md:group-odd:-translate-x-1/2 md:group-even:translate-x-1/2 ml-0 md:ml-0 z-10 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110">
        <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-cyber-yellow"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-[calc(100%-3rem)] md:w-[calc(50%-2rem)] border border-cyber-yellow/30 p-6 bg-cyber-bg-light/60 backdrop-blur-sm group-hover:border-cyber-yellow/70 transition-colors ml-4 md:ml-0 md:group-odd:mr-8 md:group-even:ml-8 relative">
        <div class="absolute -top-[1px] -left-[1px] w-4 h-4 border-t-2 border-l-2 border-cyber-yellow z-10"></div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-[1px] -right-[1px] w-4 h-4 border-b-2 border-r-2 border-cyber-yellow z-10"></div>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2 font-orbitron group-hover:text-shadow-[0_0_10px_var(--color-cyber-yellow)] transition-all">Виртуальный B2B-конфигураторы</h4>
        <p class="text-cyber-muted mb-4 text-sm font-sans leading-relaxed">Система параметрической 2D/3D-визуализации и автоматизированного расчета (лестницы, модульные здания).</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs font-mono">
          <span class="text-cyber-magenta">Vue 3</span>
          <span class="text-cyber-cyan">Canvas/WebGL</span>
          <span class="text-cyber-yellow">Node.js</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Item 4 -->
    <div class="relative flex items-center justify-between md:justify-normal md:odd:flex-row-reverse group border-yellow">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-cyber-green bg-cyber-bg text-cyber-green shrink-0 md:order-1 md:group-odd:-translate-x-1/2 md:group-even:translate-x-1/2 ml-0 md:ml-0 z-10 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110">
        <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-cyber-green"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-[calc(100%-3rem)] md:w-[calc(50%-2rem)] border border-cyber-green/30 p-6 bg-cyber-bg-light/60 backdrop-blur-sm group-hover:border-cyber-green/70 transition-colors ml-4 md:ml-0 md:group-odd:mr-8 md:group-even:ml-8 relative">
        <div class="absolute -top-[1px] -left-[1px] w-4 h-4 border-t-2 border-l-2 border-cyber-green z-10"></div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-[1px] -right-[1px] w-4 h-4 border-b-2 border-r-2 border-cyber-green z-10"></div>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2 font-orbitron group-hover:text-shadow-[0_0_10px_var(--color-cyber-green)] transition-all">Сайтик — PWA-конструктор</h4>
        <p class="text-cyber-muted mb-4 text-sm font-sans leading-relaxed">Full-stack: минималистичный конструктор для создания связанных гипертекстовых архивов.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs font-mono">
          <span class="text-cyber-magenta">Vue 3</span>
          <span class="text-cyber-cyan">PWA</span>
          <span class="text-cyber-yellow">MongoDB</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
